form creation and the ORM migrations.

00:07:37.240 --> 00:07:39.220
All that stuff is kind of just, you get it all.

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:42.880
And the other end, you have Flask and you have FastAPI

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:46.680
and a whole bunch of others, Sanic, you name it.

